  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this randomized controlled trial the utility of capnography and IPI gets evaluated.
      Hypoxemia may occur during sedation with midazolam and propofol. Whether hypoxemia may be
      prevented by an additional capnographic monitoring is subject of the study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
